[A changing medical and economic world: complex diseases and interest in 
economic evaluation of health technologies].

[Article in French]

Hiligsmann M(1), Reginster JY.

Author information:
(1)Département de Santé Publique, d'Epidémiologie et d'Economie de la Santé, 
